    <main>
      <div data-l="zh">
        <span class="fp-eyebrow">复验教程 · Verify</span>
        <h1>亲手复验一局牌</h1>
        <p class="fp-lead">两步走：先确认线上客户端与公开核心源码一致，再用本地 verifier 重放你下载的牌局记录。不需要相信我们——你自己跑一遍。</p>
      </div>
      <div data-l="en">
        <span class="fp-eyebrow">Verify</span>
        <h1>Verify a hand yourself</h1>
        <p class="fp-lead">Two steps: first confirm the live client matches the public core source, then replay your downloaded hand transcript with the local verifier. You don't have to trust us — run it yourself.</p>
      </div>

      <section data-release-facts>
        <h2><span data-l="zh">发布事实</span><span data-l="en">Release facts</span></h2>
        <dl class="fp-dl">
          <dt>Official domain</dt><dd>https://fairpoker.app</dd>
          <dt>Game client CID</dt><dd><span data-release-field="gameClientCid">Read from canonical release JSON</span></dd>
          <dt>Source package CID</dt><dd><span data-release-field="sourceCid">Read from canonical release JSON</span></dd>
          <dt>Source package URL</dt><dd><span data-release-field="sourceArchiveUrl">Read from canonical release JSON</span></dd>
          <dt>Source fingerprint</dt><dd><span data-release-field="sourceFingerprint">Read from canonical release JSON</span></dd>
          <dt>Archive SHA256</dt><dd><span data-release-field="archiveSha256">Read from canonical release JSON</span></dd>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <div data-l="zh">
        <h3><span class="fp-step" aria-hidden="true">1</span>确认线上前端 = 公开核心代码</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>确认你进入的牌局客户端 CID 等于上面的 Game client CID。用 <code>ipfs.io</code>、<code>dweb.link</code> 等不同网关打开同一 CID，应得到同一份前端文件。</li>
          <li>下载核心源码审计包，校验压缩包 SHA256 是否等于上面的 Archive SHA256。</li>
          <li>解压后重新生成源码指纹，确认输出与上面的 Source fingerprint 一致。</li>
        </ol>
        <pre><code>curl -L -o release.json https://fairpoker.app/source/release.json
SOURCE_ARCHIVE_URL=$(node -e "console.log(require('./release.json').archiveUrl)")
ARCHIVE_SHA256=$(node -e "console.log(require('./release.json').archiveSha256.replace(/^sha256:/, ''))")

curl -L -o fair-poker-source.tar.gz "$SOURCE_ARCHIVE_URL"

shasum -a 256 fair-poker-source.tar.gz
# 应等于 $ARCHIVE_SHA256

mkdir fair-poker-source
tar -xzf fair-poker-source.tar.gz -C fair-poker-source --strip-components=1
cd fair-poker-source
npm ci
npm run generate:release-metadata
grep sourceFingerprint src/generated/releaseMetadata.ts</code></pre>
        <p>如果 SHA256 与 Source fingerprint 都一致，说明公开的发牌、洗牌、加密、解密、签名、transcript 与 verifier 代码没有被替换。</p>

        <h3><span class="fp-step" aria-hidden="true">2</span>复验一局牌</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>在牌桌左上角打开「安全牌局」面板。</li>
          <li>点「下载」，保存本局 transcript JSON。</li>
          <li>在核心源码目录安装依赖，运行 verifier。</li>
        </ol>
        <pre><code>npm ci
npm run verify:transcript -- /path/to/transcript.json</code></pre>
        <div class="fp-callout"><p>输出通过，即代表本局的 hash-chain、事件顺序、签名格式、下注、奖池与结果都能在你本机重放复验。篡改 transcript 中任意关键字段，verifier 会报错或给出警告。</p></div>
      </div>

      <div data-l="en">
        <h3><span class="fp-step" aria-hidden="true">1</span>Match the live client to the public source</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Confirm the table client CID you opened equals the Game client CID above. The same CID should load identical frontend files through different IPFS gateways (<code>ipfs.io</code>, <code>dweb.link</code>).</li>
          <li>Download the core source audit package and compare its SHA256 with the Archive SHA256 above.</li>
          <li>Extract it, regenerate the source fingerprint, and compare it with the published Source fingerprint.</li>
        </ol>
        <pre><code>curl -L -o release.json https://fairpoker.app/source/release.json
SOURCE_ARCHIVE_URL=$(node -e "console.log(require('./release.json').archiveUrl)")
ARCHIVE_SHA256=$(node -e "console.log(require('./release.json').archiveSha256.replace(/^sha256:/, ''))")

curl -L -o fair-poker-source.tar.gz "$SOURCE_ARCHIVE_URL"

shasum -a 256 fair-poker-source.tar.gz
# must equal $ARCHIVE_SHA256

mkdir fair-poker-source
tar -xzf fair-poker-source.tar.gz -C fair-poker-source --strip-components=1
cd fair-poker-source
npm ci
npm run generate:release-metadata
grep sourceFingerprint src/generated/releaseMetadata.ts</code></pre>
        <p>If both the archive SHA256 and Source fingerprint match, the public dealing, shuffling, encryption, decryption, signing, transcript, and verifier code has not been replaced.</p>

        <h3><span class="fp-step" aria-hidden="true">2</span>Replay a hand transcript</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Open the Secure Table panel in the upper-left table tools.</li>
          <li>Click Download to save the hand transcript JSON.</li>
          <li>In the core source directory, install dependencies and run the verifier.</li>
        </ol>
        <pre><code>npm ci
npm run verify:transcript -- /path/to/transcript.json</code></pre>
        <div class="fp-callout"><p>A passing result means the hand's hash-chain, event order, signature format, bets, pot, and outcome can all be replayed on your own machine. Tampering with any important transcript field makes the verifier fail or warn.</p></div>
      </div>
    </main>

